:'''Abraham:''' L&mdash;L&mdash;Left, The Hunt...
:'''Abraham:''' The Hunt on the left, Harmony on the right, and Erudition in the heart...
:{{DIcon|Arrow}} It's done.
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_200022267-->
::'''Abraham:''' I can hear something... but no matter what happens, even if I die the next second, I must finish reciting this phrase.
::'''Abraham:''' The Hunt on the left, Harmony on the right, Erudition in the heart, and Preservation on the chest!
::'''Abraham:''' Okay, well done, Abraham.
::'''Abraham:''' Wow, you are back already? I only recited this morale chant 167 times, and the Space Anchor is already activated.
:{{DIcon|Arrow}} What are you doing?
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_200022272-->
::'''Abraham:''' Hey, you're back already! So soon! I've only recited this morale chant 167 times.
::'''Abraham:''' Before you say anything, please allow me to finish reciting it, otherwise, I will feel very uncomfortable.
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} I understand!
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_200022275-->
:::'''Abraham:''' Thank you, you're very kind.
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Well, hurry up...
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_200022277-->
:::'''Abraham:''' Yes, I am going as fast as I can.
::'''Abraham:''' The Hunt on the left, Harmony on the right, Erudition in the heart, and Preservation on the chest!
::'''Abraham:''' Phew... Okay. Well done, Abraham.
::'''Abraham:''' Now, let's get back to business. I see that the Space Anchor over there has been reactivated.
:{{DIcon|Arrow}} The dragon on your chest!
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_200022282-->
::'''Abraham:''' On the chest is Preservation!
::'''Abraham:''' This is the chant of Aeon protection that I came up with myself. Please don't alter the wording, lest we offend the Aeons.
::'''Abraham:''' But I only recited this chant 167 times and you already activated the Space Anchor.
:'''Abraham:''' Actually, when I was reciting the chant, I figured it all out... Since you've helped me complete my task already, I can now continue to stay on the team. And I will eventually hunt down the monster that killed Alfred and avenge him.
:'''Abraham:''' I will prove to you that I have the courage to take that step before the long night of death.
:'''Abraham:''' I hope this is not our last encounter. Farewell, (Trailblazer)...
:<!--Ends the current performance-->
